\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \alpha_{1},\dots,\alpha_{k},\beta_{1},\dots,\beta_{n}\right\} $
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Ax_{i}=\sum_{i=1}^{k}\alpha_{i}u_{i}+\sum_{i=1}^{n}\beta_{i}v_{i}
\]

\end_inset

